Package: HFRS
Title: Hospital Frailty Risk Scores from ICD-10 codes
Version: 0.0.1.0000
Authors@R: 
    person("James", "van Oppen", , "james.vanoppen@doctors.org.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2570-7112"))
Description: Calculates Hospital Frailty Risk Scores from ICD-10 codes. Categorises HFRS risk as Low, Intermediate, or High. This package uses points data from supplementary appendices published by Gilbert T, et al. Lancet 2018; http://dx.doi.org/10.1016/S0140-6736(18)30668-8.
